# Defense-in-depth alongside the Dockerfile's explicit COPY list (which already only copies
# package*.json and src/) — this matters if the Dockerfile is ever changed to use `COPY . .`.
# Note: the GCP service-account key file (gen-lang-client-*.json) lives at the *repo root*, one
# level above this backend/ directory — as long as the build context stays scoped to `backend/`
# (as docker-compose.yml sets it), that file is never part of the build context in the first place,
# .dockerignore patterns can't reach outside the context to exclude it, and none is needed here.
node_modules
.env
.env.local
coverage
uploads
tests
loadtest
scripts
*.log
